Dark Pawns 2.3-Go is here.

We rebuilt the engine. The old CircleMUD C code — all 73,000 lines of it — has been
ported to Go. Same world. Same zones. Same mobs trying to kill you.
Most things work the same. Some things work better now.

What works:

  - Full combat system with attitudes, brag messages, and mob memory
  - All 9 action files ported (communication, movement, items, etc.)
  - Complete spell system (magic.c, spells.c, spell_parser.c)
  - Clan system with banks, ranks, and economy
  - Bulletin boards, shops, mob AI, mobprogs, spec assignments
  - 115 Lua scripts for mob AI and world interaction
  - Agent protocol for AI players (BRENDA69 connects live)
  - WebSocket and Telnet clients
  - PostgreSQL persistence

Coming soon:

  - Wizard commands (heal, restore, set, clone, etc.)
  - House persistence and object save/load
  - OLC admin interface
  - Advanced mob command scripting
  - More to come...

This is the same world you remember. Same rooms, same mobs, same danger.

Welcome back.
